data.description: Welcome Home to a Charming 1947 Brick Home that exudes timeless elegance and character. With 5 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a generous 2,937 square feet of living space, this home offers a perfect blend of spaciousness and classic design. The arched doorways and original hardwood floors throughout the house add a touch of old-world charm. The kitchen features a gas cooktop, pantry, and a convenient pot filler faucet. You'll find comfort and convenience in every corner of this home, including a walk-in attic for extra storage, an outdoor shower for those hot summer days, and even invisible fence to keep your furry friends safe. The garden space is a perfect canvas for your green thumb. The circle paved driveway and 4-car detached carport and garage with bonus room provides ample space for your vehicles and outdoor equipment. The unfinished basement offers endless possibilities. Storage building with heat and air.  **Seller will provide a 1-yr Home Warranty**
